    "Organizations must test models on specific deployment contexts and treat transparency as a distinct training objective.",
    "Some models achieving substantial disclosure demonstrates this is achievable, though room for improvement remains.Whether similar patterns exist in frontier closed-source models requires direct testing, though the shared training paradigm makes similar context-dependence plausible.",
